----------- SHERPA 1.0 ----------

Homepage: www.sherpa-mc.de
Contact : info@sherpa-mc.de
---------------------------------

The SHERPA-package is the steering unit of the
SHERPA-framework. Also, it is responsible for
the merging of the parton shower with the matrix
element which is done according to the CKKW-
algorithm. A description of this algorithm can be
found at JHEP 0111 (2001) 063 and JHEP 0208 (2002) 015.